<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>A cardigan is a warm and stylish wardrobe staple that's perfect for when the temperature drops.</p>

<p>Shoppers have been snapping up autumnal fashion essentials on Amazon, from oversized jumpers and comfy joggers to snuggly fleeces and this cosy Abollria Waterfall Cardigan.</p>

<p>Not only is the cardigan made from a warm yet lightweight blend of cotton and polyester, but it's also soft and comfortable.</p>

<p>The Abollria Waterfall Cardigan is soft, comfortable and affordable - the perfect fall staple</p>

<p>Featuring an open front that falls to the top of the knees to flatter the figure, the cardigan boasts full-length sleeves in two styles, a longline silhouette and pockets.</p>

<p>While it's still racking up reviews (800 and counting), over 60 per cent of shoppers have given it a perfect five-star rating. And at just £16.99, depending on what size and colour you pick, the Abollria Waterfall Cardigan is pretty affordable, too.</p>

<p>Customers who have tried the cardigan love that it's 'well made' and 'fits beautifully'.</p>

<p>'The lightweight woman's cardigan is perfect for any season,' raved one customer. 'Simply throw on a t-shirt underneath and wear it in a summers night, or layers it on for the winter. The beige colour goes well with anything. Cardigans are easy to dress up or down and still look great.'</p>

<p>Featuring an open front that falls to the top of the knees to flatter the figure, the cardigan has become a hit with shoppers</p>

<p>Another customer wrote: 'Great fit and looks smart. Ordered a few of these in different colours.'</p>

<p>'Great cardigan, bought for work and is perfect in style, colour fit and weight,' commented another. It's smart, easy to iron and was very good value for money.'</p>

<p>Available in ten classic neutral colours including black, beige and grey, the easy-to-wear cardigan will go with everything you in your wardrobe. Team with a white tee, jeans and boots for an effortlessly chic daytime look.</p>

